@node Chall1 "CHALLENGE ONE"
Your challenge is:

Get someone else to build an extremely large house in less than two hours.

@{"Click here to begin" link Ch1}
@endnode

@node Ch1 "CHALLENGE 1"
Telephoning a large, and very expensive (very expensive), building contractors - "David Wilson Homes"
(Please note: There is no connection with the 'real' David Wilson Homes - any references are purely fictional, etc...)

<RING RING> <RING RING>

Some bloke answers... "Hello.  David Wilson Homes.  How can I help you?"

@{"1. Hello, this is Annie from the 'Challenge' programme...             " link Ch11}
@{"2. Can I speak to David Wilson please?                                " link Ch12}
@{"3. Can-you-build-me-an-extremely-big-house-for-free-you'll-get-on-the-" link Ch1111}
@{"   telly-honest-guv?" link Ch1111}

(Choose a response by clicking on the appropiate text)
@endnode
INPUT A

